videos.description: Connor Crabtree whips a pass down low to Blake Paul, who gathers and finishes with a thunderous two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Tulane jumps ahead on Paul's big slam

videos.description: Mfiondu Kabengele gets around Buay Koka and powers through the contact for the bucket and a foul.
videos.headline: Kabengele spins for and-1

videos.description: Raiquan Gray is left all alone at the rim, but he inexplicably loses the ball as he rises up for the easy finish.
videos.headline: Gray blows dunk in embarrassing fashion

videos.description: Trent Forrest intercepts a Tulane pass and takes it the length of the floor for a nice fast-break finish.
videos.headline: Forrest steals and scores

videos.description: Trent Forrest drives the lane and throws a pass behind Samir Sehic's back, setting up Mfiondu Kabengele's big finish.
videos.headline: Forrest sets up Kabengele with crafty wrap-around pass

videos.description: Trent Forrest drops a pass to Christ Koumadje, who gets Jordan Cornish in the air and puts away an emphatic jam.
videos.headline: Koumadje throws down two-handed slam
